Yo, long time, no see, [[man|Find The Others]]. It's kinda surreal speaking with you. I've been stupidly busy,<<ref "t">> and I want to attempt to give you some [[fitted context|Help]] to think about what you are looking at more generally in this wiki. I am required to build doorways for people into this [[monster]].

<<<
Hey h0p3,

It's great to hear from you.
<<<

Good, I'm glad! Not everyone enjoys hearing from me.<<ref "s">> I'm glad to [[hear|Contact]] from [[you|BL]], too. I've been working on maintaining remote relationships over the past few years and this wiki is my primary tool.<<ref "h">> Like a madman, I scribble in the open.

<<<
Thanks for the congratulations.
<<<

You've been on quite a journey and I only understand the bare outlines of it. Back 15 years ago, I think I would have been surprised to find out we would be in our particular shoes today. I'm glad to see you kicking ass. I'm excited to see what the future holds for you.

<<<
I apologize for not getting back to you sooner.
<<<

Ah, please don't worry about it. First, I take forever in my [[correspondence]]. Second, I believe you've had way more important things to do with your time than send me a letter. The rate of change in the world is too much for me to fathom, though I consider it my obligation to try to understand it. I can imagine you have a ton on your plate so I'm honored that you were able to squeeze me in. 

<<<
I'm doing OK, but things have been a bit odd.
<<<

No shit, dude. Lol. I'm glad you are doing okay in the whirlwind. While I don't have enough of a record or a memory of it, I have been following HK with what resources I have.

